OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPercy Pig ice cream renamed
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fafter M&S request          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, An ice cream parlour has changed the   
OL,6, name of one its products after a       
OL,7, "polite" request from Marks & Spencer. 
OL,9,FFabio's Gelato, based in Hitchin,      
OL,10,FHertfordshire, only began making its   
OL,11,FPercy Pig ice cream last week.         
OL,13,FBut the retailing giant sent the owner 
OL,14,FFabio Vincenti a letter which said he  
OL,15,Fcould continue to use the sweets, but  
OL,16,Fnot the name of the product.           
OL,18,F"It is what it is, they've got to      
OL,19,Fprotect Percy Pig," he said.           
